{{Use Indian English|date=June 2018}}
'''Chaugan Stadium''' is a stadium in [[Jaipur]] city in [[Rajasthan]] state in [[India]]. [[Elephant polo]] matches are played here. The stadium is venue of [[Teej]] festivities and [[Elephant Festival]]. The stadium lies between Gangauri Bazaar and the [[City Palace, Jaipur|City Palace]] not far away from [[Govind Dev Ji Temple]].

